                            <li>Tournament admins have the final say in all disputes</li>
                            <li>Teams must be ready 15 minutes before their scheduled match time</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-[#ff4655]">Match Format</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
                            <li>Quarter Finals and Semi Finals: Best of 1</li>
                            <li>Finals: Best of 3</li>
                            <li>Map selection will be done through veto system</li>
                            <li>Standard competitive rules apply</li>
                            <li>Teams have 5 minutes between maps in Finals</li>
                            <li>15 minute grace period for scheduled matches</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-[#ff4655]">Technical Requirements</h3>
