                            <li>Discord is mandatory for communication with tournament admins</li>
                            <li>Players must be able to stream their gameplay if requested</li>
                            <li>Latest game patch must be installed</li>
                            <li>In-game voice chat is allowed for team communication</li>
                            <li>Any technical issues must be reported immediately to admins</li>
